# Parked research artifact: do not commit the lockfile. It is regenerable via
# `npm install` (see README). Keeping it out of git keeps this off-app prototype
# out of the repo dependency graph, so Dependabot does not raise security alerts
# for its transitive deps. The `overrides` in package.json still pins the
# security floor (e.g. underscore >=1.13.8) for anyone who regenerates it.
package-lock.json
